22	TCP	SSH/SFTP	Secure Shell or FTP over SSH
23	TCP	TELNET	Unsecure remote administration
25	TCP	SMTP	Simple Mail Transfer Protocol
53	TCP/UDP	DNS	Domain Name System (TCP for zone transfers)
67/68	UDP	DHCP	Server (67) and Client (68) ports
80/443	TCP	HTTP/HTTPS	HyperText Transfer Protocol (Secure)
110/995	TCP	POP3(S)	Post Office Protocol (Secure)
135-139	Various	NetBIOS/RPC	Windows/UNIX RPC and legacy file sharing
